&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-js s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0.1&lt;/span&gt; + &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0.2&lt;/span&gt;         -&amp;gt;  &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-number&quot;&gt;0.30000000000000004&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Why do these inaccuracies happen?&lt;/p&gt;
